## COMPONENTES — PADRÕES OBRIGATÓRIOS

### Sidebar pill animada
```tsx
// UMA div absoluta que se move — não remova/adicione classes nos itens
<nav className="relative">
  <div 
    id="nav-pill"
    className="absolute left-3 right-3 rounded-[14px] bg-limao-500 transition-[top] duration-300"
    style={{ top: activePillTop, height: activePillHeight }}
  />
  {navItems.map(item => (
    <button
      key={item.id}
      ref={item.ref}  // necessário para calcular posição
      onClick={() => setActive(item.id)}
      className="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-3.5 px-4 py-3 w-full rounded-[18px]"
    >
      <item.Icon size={20} className={isActive ? 'text-ink-500' : 'text-base-700'} />
      <span className={`text-[18px] font-semibold tracking-[0.3px] ${isActive ? 'text-ink-500' : 'text-base-700'}`}>
        {item.label}
      </span>
    </button>
  ))}
</nav>
```

### Tabs com pill
```tsx
// Mesma lógica: UMA div se move horizontalmente
<div className="relative flex bg-base-600/30 rounded-[10px] p-1">
  <div
    className="absolute top-1 h-[calc(100%-8px)] bg-white rounded-[8px] shadow-sm transition-[left,width] duration-300"
    style={{ left: pillLeft, width: pillWidth }}
  />
  {tabs.map(tab => (
    <button key={tab.id} ref={tab.ref} onClick={() => selectTab(tab.id)}
      className="relative z-10 px-[18px] py-2 text-[14px] font-semibold">
      {tab.label}
    </button>
  ))}
</div>
```

